name: pow_oofr
jaxpr:
{ lambda ; a:f32[15,14] b:f32[15,14]. let
    c:f32[15,14] = abs a
    d:f32[15,14] = abs b
    e:f32[15,14] = jit[
      name=remainder
      jaxpr={ lambda ; d:f32[15,14] f:i32[]. let
          g:f32[] = convert_element_type[new_dtype=float32 weak_type=False] f
          h:f32[15,14] = rem d g
          i:bool[15,14] = ne h 0.0:f32[]
          j:bool[15,14] = lt h 0.0:f32[]
          k:bool[] = lt g 0.0:f32[]
          l:bool[15,14] = ne j k
          m:bool[15,14] = and l i
          n:f32[15,14] = add h g
          e:f32[15,14] = select_n m h n
        in (e,) }
    ] d 3:i32[]
    o:f32[15,14] = add e 1.0:f32[]
    p:f32[15,14] = pow c o
  in (p,) }
